==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tentaculite
<hw>Ten*tac"u*lite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Paleon.)</fld>
<def>Any one of numerous species of small, conical fossil shells found
in Paleozoic rocks. They are supposed to be pteropods.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tentaculocyst</ent>⟦br⟧
